{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":{"name":"Anubhav Srivastava","contacts":{"twitter":"onlyanubhav"}},"disqusShortname":"theanubhav","subtitle":"Personal quick tips for Web Developers","title":"Quick Dev tips by Anubhav Srivastava","url":"http://devtips.theanubhav.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ccdaf915-ed61-564f-8e7d-506d4188afb2","html":"<p>This is a series of libraries and utilities for building Command-line-interfaces aka CLI using Node.js and ecosystem around it. Similar utilities/helpers may be available for other languages but, these series is focused on JavaScript and its friends.</p>\n<p>You can check all articles under <a href=\"/category/cli-build-tool/\"><code class=\"language-text\">CLI Build Tool</code></a> tag.</p>\n<h2 id=\"node-notifier\"><a href=\"#node-notifier\" aria-label=\"node notifier permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/mikaelbr/node-notifier\">node-notifier</a></h2>\n<p>If you are building a CLI and need to show notification to user to make your CLI more interactive and user friendly, <code class=\"language-text\">node-notifier</code> is the package you need. Of course, it is cross-platform and you can send notifications on native Mac, Windows and Linux.</p>\n<p><em>on Mac</em>\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/83a56cfa009df9011b55c309d30b16f4/17294/nodenotifier1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 326px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 19.938650306748468%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/83a56cfa009df9011b55c309d30b16f4/17294/nodenotifier1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/83a56cfa009df9011b55c309d30b16f4/0783d/nodenotifier1.png 240w,\n/static/83a56cfa009df9011b55c309d30b16f4/17294/nodenotifier1.png 326w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><em>on Windows</em>\n<a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9b017de93143c68386899dab1fce05d8/0c144/nodenotifier2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 234px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 27.77777777777778%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9b017de93143c68386899dab1fce05d8/0c144/nodenotifier2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9b017de93143c68386899dab1fce05d8/0c144/nodenotifier2.png 234w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 234px) 100vw, 234px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>For instance, if your CLI watches a file (like <code class=\"language-text\">chowkidar</code>) and takes an action (like restarting a service or rebuilding your project), you can notify using system notifications along with CLI output.</p>\n<p>Input Example macOS Notification Center\n<img src=\"/node-notifier-e640acc7a8fc6be16b1f4ded82711fa4.gif\" alt=\"Screenshot\"></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">node-notifier</code> has a very easy to follow, simple to use API. Here is a code example:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> notifier <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'node-notifier'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// String</span>\nnotifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">notify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Object</span>\nnotifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">notify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\ttitle<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'My notification'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tmessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hello, there!'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>There are a lot of conditions and scenarios for cross platform implementation of this module.\nYou can check out official <a href=\"https://github.com/mikaelbr/node-notifier\">repo</a> for all usage details.</p>\n<p>Github Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/mikaelbr/node-notifier\">node-notifier</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"related\"><a href=\"#related\" aria-label=\"related permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Check <a href=\"https://github.com/mikaelbr/node-notifier-cli\">node-notifier-cli</a> - CLI version for this module</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/cli-node-notifier","tagSlugs":["/tag/cli/","/tag/tools/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-06-30T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Node.js CLI App helper for showing notifications","tags":["CLI","Tools"],"title":"Tool of the Trade for CLI Apps - `node-notifier`  ðŸ“º"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/cli-node-notifier"}}